title: This Month's GTA+ Membership Benefits
headline: This Month's GTA+ Membership Benefits
subtitle: This Month's GTA+ Membership Benefits
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposit directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ members who've signed up for this month (April 13 - May 10) will also receive:

- The Karin Boor Off-Road vehicle
- The Paleto Bay Meth Lab with a free staff upgrade
- New Chameleon Paints
- Spatter weapon finishes
- Bonus Rewards for Acid Lab Sell Missions
- And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
